*魯道夫2007星座好運全記錄（書內插圖繪畫）<ref>[http://education.atnext.com/index.cfm?fuseaction=Article.View&articleID=10275543&issueID=20071011 人脈關係廣$0做洋蔥頭代理] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071013065559/http://education.atnext.com/index.cfm?fuseaction=Article.View&articleID=10275543&issueID=20071011 |date=2007-10-13 }}，壹學堂，2007年10月11日</ref>
